The incident occurred during the early hours of this morning between Riversdale and the Stilbaai turnoff. CAPE TOWN Five people have been killed following a collision on the N1 in the Western Cape.The incident occurred during the early hours of this morning between Riversdale and the Stilbaai turnoff.The highway remains closed off in both directions.Western Cape traffic chief Kenny Africa said, The vehicle was burnt completely and all four occupants of the car were burnt beyond recognition and the other person from the other car died. 